\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Novelty-frontier band assignments and score distribution. (a)~Band assignment by model: responses are concentrated in low-novelty and frontier-proximal bands across all seven architectures, indicating architecture-independent constraint patterns rather than isolated model failures. (b)~Overall continuous novelty score distribution with KDE overlay; dashed line marks the median.}}{8}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:frontier_bands}{{2}{8}{Novelty-frontier band assignments and score distribution. (a)~Band assignment by model: responses are concentrated in low-novelty and frontier-proximal bands across all seven architectures, indicating architecture-independent constraint patterns rather than isolated model failures. (b)~Overall continuous novelty score distribution with KDE overlay; dashed line marks the median}{figure.2}{}}
